{"tid":2082551,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"原來三綱五常係咁，依家完全被人扭曲哂","createTime":"2020-06-28T06:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T06:53:07.000Z","uid":262674,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3e5213f2f9b0a2aa2f0fbf9c32daab3b633fcd0d","tid":2082551,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T06:16:47.000Z","msg":"君為臣綱，君不正，臣投他國。國為民綱，國不正，民起攻之。父為子綱，父不慈，子奔他鄉。子為父望，子不正，大義滅親。夫為妻綱，夫不正，妻可改嫁。妻為夫助，妻不賢，夫則休之。五常為：愛之仁，正之義，君之禮，哲思智，情同信。（出自《韓非子&middot;忠孝》）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家變哂做愚忠愚孝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部只講第一句<br />\n原來後面係重點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0a1c8b6592060dd9b11e21fcbe4546861183fa","tid":2082551,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T06:21:54.000Z","msg":"左膠思想"},{"pid":"492206be0300be585af091a0ddbd7da479587674","tid":2082551,"uid":26385,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T06:22:14.000Z","msg":"俾當權者扭曲曬<br />\n成段野個中心思想都係如果你做唔好你應該做嘅野，人地就有legitimacy去收你皮<br />\n以當年嚟講咁嘅思想係領先全世界<br />\n但奈何講一回事，做又另一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ccf5aedbe609f00185d8813f1b8dd088dfb207","tid":2082551,"uid":46151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T06:24:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ctext.org/hanfeizi/zhong-xiao/zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fctext.org%2Fhanfeizi%2Fzhong-xiao%2Fzh&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtIgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=9c402e05\" target=\"_blank\">https://ctext.org/hanfeizi/zhong-xiao/zh</a><br />\n韓非子幾時有呢段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053fb253f708daf5d0dfb183d97ca24dabb76e64","tid":2082551,"uid":262674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"99ccf5aedbe609f00185d8813f1b8dd088dfb207","tid":2082551,"uid":46151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T06:24:04.000Z","msg":"<a